The Glenn Beck Program

      The Glenn Beck Program - 3/19/14Wednesday, March 19, 2014 11:09 AM



Glenn is astonished that Michelle Obama's agenda on food has caused
     The head pastry chef at the White House to quit
       citing his refusal to "demonize" eggs, sugar, flour and cream. 

 Also, is Stu leaving the GB show, and what is Glenn's new musical obsession? 

 Plus, Greg Bannon joins the program to discuss 
        his Senate run for the seat of North Carolina.
